{"tid":1925701,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★高層PK！不排除天台位置為傳播途徑","createTime":"2020-03-14T14:30:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T14:35:18.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c0c0954c88e493bd11ec3876d42071d493e51ed8","tid":1925701,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T14:30:18.000Z","msg":"袁國勇表示，現階段未找到事件原因，相關情況仍在調查中，但指兩個單位的喉管、建築設計都沒有問題，只是32樓住戶的排氣管折斷後只用膠紙封住，強調情況肯定不是淘大和康美樓翻版。<br />\n專家觀察情況後認為或是32樓的糞便裏的病毒霧化後，經排氣喉升上天台，一般會經空氣稀釋，但如風勢微弱，或有可能有建築物擾流效應，將排氣喉的氣體帶回入屋，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不排除天台位置為傳播途徑</span>，因此防護中心將頂6層的住戶送往隔離，但他指專家計算後料最多影響5層住戶。<br />\n<br />\n謝展寰表示，不能排除透過糞渠傳染的可能性，政府會派人檢查其他單位有否把排氣管改裝或切斷，而調查的另一方向是兩個單位糞渠的通氣位亦在天台，會在天台不同地方採摘樣本調查是否由風吹病毒入屋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200314/bkn-20200314163642911-0314_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200314%2Fbkn-20200314163642911-0314_00822_001.html&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=9a0e7efb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200314/bkn-20200314163642911-0314_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"14ef3eb04aa2259ac83908d391dcc5ca991659d4","tid":1925701,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T14:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ddf1f2ad2f5360b04d9aed1c102f92f260da2d","tid":1925701,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T14:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b0c487ca3eae9cb8756031ffebb0be8264193d","tid":1925701,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T14:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得公屋(低層)得天下"}]}